textContent:
---sweater weather---

We've experienced our first rainy season together bby!! Hehehe ang comfy talaga ng weather lalo pag kasama kita. I feel like I could sleep all day just cuddling up with you and kissing you and your cheeks and your tummy and your pata. I love how I crave for your presence every time it rains because I know how comfortable I could get when I'm with you.

MWAA!! I'm so happy that this is just the first of the many rainy seasons we'll spend together! I can't wait for the day na sabay na tayong gigising to the sound of the rain tas sabay tayong magkakape tas sabay ulit rayo kakain ng rolling hot pandesal huhuhu. 

Thank you for existing, my bbycakes! I love you so much! You make the bad weather good with your presence alone!
